34
00:02:14,540 --> 00:02:16,460
It’s late. You may leave.

35
00:02:17,580 --> 00:02:19,220
We still have other things to discuss.

36
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:22,100
Yes, Your Majesty.

37
00:02:25,580 --> 00:02:26,300
Let’s go.

38
00:02:40,740 --> 00:02:41,580
- Today... - Today.

39
00:02:47,780 --> 00:02:49,020
You first, Danshu.

40
00:02:57,260 --> 00:02:58,060
Your Majesty,

41
00:03:03,460 --> 00:03:04,860
am I

42
00:03:05,420 --> 00:03:07,780
too strict and rigid

43
00:03:09,780 --> 00:03:13,860
when managing the harem?

44
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:18,740
That girl

45
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:21,100
was passionate and energetic.

46
00:03:26,860 --> 00:03:28,780
Perhaps in your eyes,

47
00:03:29,340 --> 00:03:30,340
members led by me in the harem

48
00:03:31,900 --> 00:03:33,580
are as dull

49
00:03:33,580 --> 00:03:34,420
as puppets.

50
00:03:35,780 --> 00:03:36,580
Danshu.

51
00:03:38,180 --> 00:03:39,980
I have no discontent with you.

52
00:03:42,620 --> 00:03:44,780
Shortly after you took charge at 18,

53
00:03:45,460 --> 00:03:47,060
you were respected

54
00:03:47,140 --> 00:03:48,180
and supported by all.

55
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:51,100
I don’t manage the harem,

56
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:53,020
but I’m not ignorant.

57
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:55,260
Had you lacked lenience

58
00:03:55,460 --> 00:03:56,700
or talents,

59
00:03:57,140 --> 00:03:58,740
and only followed in others’ steps,

60
00:03:59,260 --> 00:04:00,660
others wouldn’t have respected you.

61
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:04,860
To be honest,

62
00:04:05,220 --> 00:04:07,620
I didn’t follow the rules when I was little.

63
00:04:08,620 --> 00:04:09,340
I...

64
00:04:09,340 --> 00:04:10,180
I know.

65
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:13,780
You were well-versed in riding and fencing

66
00:04:14,820 --> 00:04:16,580
and you sneaked into the Nanjing Academy

67
00:04:16,740 --> 00:04:17,620
to attend lectures.

68
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:21,060
Rules couldn’t restrict you.

69
00:04:28,140 --> 00:04:28,980
Danshu.

70
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:34,060
I also understand

71
00:04:35,340 --> 00:04:36,620
that in this palace...

72
00:04:45,540 --> 00:04:46,180
Danshu!

73
00:04:46,180 --> 00:04:47,860
Guards! Protect His Majesty!

74
00:04:58,380 --> 00:05:00,060
Your Majesty, Your Highness,

75
00:05:00,420 --> 00:05:02,380
as Your Highness requested,

76
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:04,660
I had men go to chambers and storages

77
00:05:04,820 --> 00:05:06,260
where cotton silk, clothes,

78
00:05:06,260 --> 00:05:07,860
books and paper are stored

79
00:05:07,860 --> 00:05:08,700
to check.

80
00:05:08,940 --> 00:05:10,940
A few places did catch fire.

81
00:05:11,260 --> 00:05:12,860
Luckily, Your Highness was meticulous.

82
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:15,340
Guards and servants arrived in time

83
00:05:15,620 --> 00:05:16,620
and put off the fire.

84
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:19,060
Other than the chambers,

85
00:05:19,340 --> 00:05:20,460
check the Six Bureaus and

86
00:05:20,460 --> 00:05:21,540
the Imperial Kitchen closely as well

87
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:23,260
and see if the furniture is moved

88
00:05:23,420 --> 00:05:24,540
or the beams are loose.

89
00:05:25,260 --> 00:05:25,900
Yes.

90
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:27,940
Treat the injured as soon as possible

91
00:05:28,260 --> 00:05:29,180
if there’s any.

92
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:31,740
I’m on it.

93
00:05:37,220 --> 00:05:38,260
Your Majesty, Your Highness,

94
00:05:38,740 --> 00:05:39,900
in the two senior consorts’ places,

95
00:05:39,900 --> 00:05:41,700
other than a few broken frames and porcelains,

96
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:42,580
nobody was hurt.

97
00:05:42,740 --> 00:05:43,780
Their carriages have been moved

98
00:05:43,940 --> 00:05:45,020
to the open ground

99
00:05:45,020 --> 00:05:46,340
in front of the hall as you ordered.

100
00:05:46,540 --> 00:05:48,220
They're resting inside.

101
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:51,220
I’ve also checked Princess, too.

102
00:05:51,620 --> 00:05:53,020
Madam Miao and the babysitter

103
00:05:53,020 --> 00:05:54,620
are outside the chamber with Princess.

104
00:05:54,740 --> 00:05:55,780
She didn’t get startled

105
00:05:55,940 --> 00:05:57,020
and was in warm clothes

106
00:05:57,020 --> 00:05:58,340
and a cloak.

107
00:05:58,340 --> 00:05:59,180
She was quite calm

108
00:05:59,420 --> 00:06:00,780
and even smiled at me.

109
00:06:04,460 --> 00:06:05,860
Like father, like daughter.

110
00:06:07,380 --> 00:06:08,100
Your Highness,

111
00:06:08,620 --> 00:06:10,340
if there are no other orders,

112
00:06:10,580 --> 00:06:12,820
I’ll continue the inspection.

113
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:45,580
= Liu E =// Emperor Zhao Zhen.

114
00:06:56,100 --> 00:06:56,940
Your Majesty,

115
00:06:59,100 --> 00:07:00,940
your father has passed away.

116
00:07:20,740 --> 00:07:22,140
Minister Ding, Minister Wang.

117
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:23,180
Yes.

118
00:07:24,460 --> 00:07:26,700
Please write down

119
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:28,060
His Majesty’s edict

120
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:30,300
made orally.

121
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:32,980
Officer Lei.

122
00:07:34,260 --> 00:07:34,740
Yes.

123
00:07:35,020 --> 00:07:37,540
Once the edict is complete,

124
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:39,580
open the Inner East Gate

125
00:07:40,740 --> 00:07:43,980
and let the royal members in.

126
00:07:44,260 --> 00:07:45,020
Yes.

127
00:08:10,700 --> 00:08:11,620
Your Majesty.

128
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:14,580
Bureau of Calendar and Directorate of Astronomy

129
00:08:14,700 --> 00:08:15,860
sent messages to the Cabinet.

130
00:08:16,340 --> 00:08:17,580
= Chen Yaozuo, courtesy name Xiyuan =
The calculation shows

131
00:08:17,860 --> 00:08:19,060
the epicenter

132
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:20,580
should be Jingdong West Province.

133
00:08:21,020 --> 00:08:23,100
We had sent officials

134
00:08:23,100 --> 00:08:24,460
to check all the provinces.

135
00:08:24,740 --> 00:08:26,260
Once the calculation result was out,

136
00:08:26,660 --> 00:08:29,300
officials were dispatched immediately

137
00:08:29,300 --> 00:08:30,260
to the local transportation agency.

138
00:08:30,540 --> 00:08:31,740
Once the situation is confirmed.

139
00:08:31,980 --> 00:08:34,620
we’ll evaluate the disaster

140
00:08:34,700 --> 00:08:36,780
and arrange the relief.

141
00:08:39,180 --> 00:08:41,420
Check the river dikes

142
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:42,940
for damages.

143
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:44,940
If there is, repair it immediately.

144
00:08:45,700 --> 00:08:48,260
The flood season is a few months away,

145
00:08:48,620 --> 00:08:50,700
so no inspection has been conducted.

146
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:53,100
But heavy rains always follow the earthquake.

147
00:08:53,300 --> 00:08:54,900
If river dikes are damaged

148
00:08:54,900 --> 00:08:55,980
and collapse,

149
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:58,060
people will suffer more

150
00:08:58,260 --> 00:08:59,460
than they already have.

151
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:02,340
Your Majesty is wise and considerate.

152
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:05,220
We're ashamed.

153
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:41,300
Disasters and the epidemic are frequent.

154
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:42,460
The earthquake struck Jingdong West Province.

155
00:09:42,460 --> 00:09:43,820
And there’s the landslide

156
00:09:43,820 --> 00:09:44,700
and the Yellow River flood.

157
00:09:45,020 --> 00:09:45,940
Yet officials of both Ministries

158
00:09:45,940 --> 00:09:47,700
