159
00:09:47,700 --> 00:09:49,460
No useful decisions have been made.

160
00:09:49,620 --> 00:09:51,740
People in those areas are homeless.

161
00:09:51,980 --> 00:09:53,100
Relief supplies

162
00:09:53,180 --> 00:09:54,060
haven’t arrived.

163
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:56,900
The homeless broke into neighboring counties

164
00:09:57,180 --> 00:09:58,500
and the disease is spreading.

165
00:09:58,620 --> 00:09:59,380
Zimei.

166
00:10:01,660 --> 00:10:03,980
= Liang Huaiji =
Censor Han, Chief Fu, Scholar Su,

167
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:05,540
these are proposals from the past ten days

168
00:10:05,740 --> 00:10:06,820
the Cabinet ordered

169
00:10:07,100 --> 00:10:09,060
to be polished

170
00:10:09,100 --> 00:10:10,900
before handed in to His Majesty.

171
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:12,580
Bring them in.

172
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:31,740
Are you new here?

173
00:10:32,300 --> 00:10:33,940
I don’t recall seeing you before.

174
00:10:34,980 --> 00:10:36,860
I came to the palace a few months ago.

175
00:10:37,060 --> 00:10:38,340
After learning the rules

176
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:39,700
and passing the test,

177
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:42,260
I was assigned to the Imperial Academy.

178
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:44,740
What’s your name? How old are you?

179
00:10:45,460 --> 00:10:47,500
My surname is Liang, Liang Huaiji.

180
00:10:47,780 --> 00:10:49,180
I was born in 1027 A.D.

181
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:50,620
and I’m 11 years old.

182
00:10:51,180 --> 00:10:51,900
I see.

183
00:10:54,700 --> 00:10:55,580
Huaiji.

184
00:11:01,180 --> 00:11:01,940
Come here.

185
00:11:10,460 --> 00:11:11,300
It’s raining heavily.

186
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:12,620
We’re shorthanded.

187
00:11:13,100 --> 00:11:14,740
Copy a few proposals for me.

188
00:11:23,220 --> 00:11:23,980
Here you are.

189
00:11:26,180 --> 00:11:26,940
Yes.

190
00:11:34,060 --> 00:11:34,860
You can do it over there.

191
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:42,380
= Bao’an’s Report about Shanyu=

192
00:11:42,420 --> 00:11:45,580
= Yan Shu, courtesy name Tongshu =

193
00:11:48,340 --> 00:11:50,300
You’ve become more composed

194
00:11:51,380 --> 00:11:52,780
and careful with words

195
00:11:53,180 --> 00:11:54,700
when giving advice.

196
00:11:56,020 --> 00:11:58,340
I’m almost 50 years old

197
00:11:58,380 --> 00:11:59,580
and have served two emperors.

198
00:11:59,980 --> 00:12:01,620
Right now, as the head of Censorate,

199
00:12:02,420 --> 00:12:04,700
I’m responsible for monitoring all officials.

200
00:12:04,900 --> 00:12:06,660
Your Majesty trusts me,

201
00:12:07,100 --> 00:12:08,460
so whatever I say and do

202
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:10,900
are considered as standards,

203
00:12:11,260 --> 00:12:12,300
as well as

204
00:12:12,380 --> 00:12:14,620
references to Your Majesty’s preferences.

205
00:12:15,660 --> 00:12:17,500
How could I not be careful?

206
00:12:29,060 --> 00:12:30,740
The Dragon Ball Tea just arrived.

207
00:12:32,180 --> 00:12:34,060
Before I invited you here,

208
00:12:34,860 --> 00:12:35,900
I especially

209
00:12:36,340 --> 00:12:38,460
asked Maoze to come from the Inner East Gate.

210
00:12:39,940 --> 00:12:42,260
I remember when I lived in the Eastern Palace,

211
00:12:42,660 --> 00:12:43,980
it was snowing outside.

212
00:12:45,180 --> 00:12:47,380
You watched me practicing my handwriting

213
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:49,620
and told me where I should improve

214
00:12:50,380 --> 00:12:53,260
while teaching Maoze

215
00:12:53,420 --> 00:12:56,660
how to pick the coal, boil water and make tea.

216
00:12:58,380 --> 00:12:59,260
I thought

217
00:13:00,060 --> 00:13:02,140
out there at court,

218
00:13:02,260 --> 00:13:03,300
you were Deputy Censor Yan

219
00:13:03,500 --> 00:13:05,820
and behind these curtains,

220
00:13:06,260 --> 00:13:07,660
you’d always be my teacher

221
00:13:08,060 --> 00:13:09,580
and be completely honest

222
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:10,540
with me.

223
00:13:11,180 --> 00:13:13,820
You’d never tiptoe around me.

224
00:13:16,900 --> 00:13:19,780
I choose my words carefully

225
00:13:21,140 --> 00:13:22,540
because

226
00:13:23,100 --> 00:13:24,220
I am in awe

227
00:13:24,460 --> 00:13:27,020
of Your Majesty day by day.

228
00:13:29,900 --> 00:13:31,620
I've never punished anyone

229
00:13:31,620 --> 00:13:32,340
because of wrong advice,

230
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:33,540
not to mention you.

231
00:13:33,860 --> 00:13:34,900
What do you fear?

232
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:38,540
Fear comes from respect.

233
00:13:39,380 --> 00:13:41,340
Your Majesty

234
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:43,140
has become an excellent emperor

235
00:13:43,700 --> 00:13:45,980
and can make your own decisions.

236
00:13:46,460 --> 00:13:47,820
You’re no longer

237
00:13:48,020 --> 00:13:49,100
a child who needs my protection

238
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:50,500
and guidance.

239
00:13:51,700 --> 00:13:54,020
If I treated you as before,

240
00:13:54,460 --> 00:13:55,620
that would be disrespectful

241
00:13:56,660 --> 00:13:58,500
and redundant.

242
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:06,940
You're right.

243
00:14:08,260 --> 00:14:09,500
When I was six,

244
00:14:09,860 --> 00:14:11,740
you taught me The Book of Rites.

245
00:14:13,260 --> 00:14:15,820
Of course you couldn’t act against it.

246
00:14:19,940 --> 00:14:22,700
Alright. Enough of the past.

247
00:14:24,020 --> 00:14:25,060
Let’s talk business.

248
00:14:26,220 --> 00:14:27,100
Please have some tea.

249
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:32,940
Zhao Yuanhao’s uncle Shanyu

250
00:14:33,140 --> 00:14:34,940
brought his family, treasures and horses

251
00:14:35,180 --> 00:14:36,780
to Bao’an for asylum.

252
00:14:36,940 --> 00:14:39,020
He claimed that Yuanhao would revolt

253
00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:40,540
and promised

254
00:14:41,260 --> 00:14:43,500
that he’d work with his old allies against him.

255
00:14:44,980 --> 00:14:46,140
Bao’an didn’t accept him

256
00:14:46,620 --> 00:14:48,300
and sent him back.

257
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:52,060
Yet, Yuanhao ambushed

258
00:14:52,620 --> 00:14:53,540
and killed him on the way.

259
00:14:54,340 --> 00:14:55,340
What do you think?

260
00:14:59,020 --> 00:15:00,620
Yuanhao will soon

261
00:15:00,940 --> 00:15:02,300
rebel against us.

262
00:15:03,980 --> 00:15:05,740
All provinces

263
00:15:05,740 --> 00:15:07,620
should be well-prepared.

264
00:15:08,260 --> 00:15:10,100
Send spies to collect information

265
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:12,980
and strengthen the security at the border

266
00:15:13,540 --> 00:15:14,660
in case of attacks.

267
00:15:15,340 --> 00:15:17,220
All departments should discuss

268
00:15:18,460 --> 00:15:19,780
the response

269
00:15:20,380 --> 00:15:22,020
if Yuanhao proclaims himself emperor.

270
00:15:26,220 --> 00:15:27,260
You saw

271
00:15:27,620 --> 00:15:29,500
the date on the report.

272
00:15:31,060 --> 00:15:32,260
After the report

273
00:15:33,060 --> 00:15:35,180
arrived at the Ministries,

274
00:15:35,580 --> 00:15:36,980
it was buried

275
00:15:37,140 --> 00:15:38,660
with other unimportant files

276
00:15:38,660 --> 00:15:40,380
for over a month.

277
00:15:40,620 --> 00:15:41,660
When it was about to be discussed,

278
00:15:42,140 --> 00:15:43,700
the earthquake happened,

279
00:15:43,940 --> 00:15:45,260
so it was delayed till a few days ago

280
00:15:45,660 --> 00:15:46,780
that Wang Sui

281
00:15:46,780 --> 00:15:48,220
and Chen Yaozuo finally processed it.

282
00:15:48,860 --> 00:15:49,740
You saw

283
00:15:50,140 --> 00:15:51,580
what they wrote.

284
00:15:52,860 --> 00:15:53,820
Ministries are unable

285
00:15:54,100 --> 00:15:56,020
to come up with relief strategies

286
00:15:56,220 --> 00:15:57,860
or military tactics

287
00:15:57,860 --> 00:15:59,340
to cope with the emergency in the west.

288
00:16:00,420 --> 00:16:01,340
After Song Qi

289
00:16:01,340 --> 00:16:03,180
and Su Shunqin expressed their complaints,

290
00:16:03,700 --> 00:16:06,140
Wang Sui claimed to be ill.

291
00:16:06,340 --> 00:16:08,180
Medicine is boiled in the Cabinet every day.

292
00:16:09,780 --> 00:16:11,300
The cabinet

293
00:16:11,300 --> 00:16:12,140
has become

294
00:16:12,820 --> 00:16:14,180
a home for the old and sick

295
00:16:14,660 --> 00:16:16,420
where their students can visit.

296
00:16:18,220 --> 00:16:19,380
Internally, the administration

297
00:16:20,660 --> 00:16:22,380
failed to provide disaster relief.

298
00:16:24,180 --> 00:16:25,540
It’s even worse externally.

299
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:30,660
Zhao Shanyu killed by Yuanhao

300
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:31,860
is a huge matter,

301
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:33,460
yet the Ministries only said

302
00:16:34,020 --> 00:16:35,260
that since Yuanhao’s father Deming

303
00:16:35,260 --> 00:16:36,340
surrendered,

304
00:16:36,380 --> 00:16:38,260
others seeking asylum due to internal strife

305
00:16:38,300 --> 00:16:39,300
have all been rejected.

306
00:16:40,030 --> 00:16:41,780
Bao’an only followed the precedent.

307
00:16:42,140 --> 00:16:44,420
Yuanhao killed Shanyu at the Sheyi Slope.

308
00:16:45,420 --> 00:16:46,340
That’s all.

309
00:16:46,660 --> 00:16:47,940
No other arrangements were made.

310
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,380
They’re shortsighted.

311
00:16:53,020 --> 00:16:55,660
You know both Minister Wang and Minister Chen

312
00:16:55,820 --> 00:16:57,860
believe that Yuanhao’s father Deming

313
00:16:57,980 --> 00:16:59,380
surrendered himself sincerely,

314
00:17:00,070 --> 00:17:03,030
stating that Zhao Deming was clement

315
00:17:03,030 --> 00:17:03,740
and unwarlike

316
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:05,300
who was completely different

317
00:17:06,780 --> 00:17:08,380
from his father Jiqian.

318
00:17:08,980 --> 00:17:09,700
Also,

319
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:11,820
they said Deming

320
00:17:11,900 --> 00:17:14,540
was cultivated by our rules and ethics

321
00:17:14,620 --> 00:17:18,140
and became all virtuous.

322
00:17:22,020 --> 00:17:22,980
Zimei,

323
00:17:23,780 --> 00:17:24,340
you...

324
00:17:29,180 --> 00:17:30,660
The Jingdong West Province earthquake

325
00:17:30,660 --> 00:17:31,420
was actually

326
00:17:31,860 --> 00:17:34,780
handled according to the rules.

327
00:17:35,860 --> 00:17:39,380
The Cabinet followed the precedents.

328
00:17:39,860 --> 00:17:41,940
There was no delay on purpose

329
00:17:42,380 --> 00:17:43,660
or embezzlement.

330
00:17:44,180 --> 00:17:47,740
Dilatoriness and inadequacy

331
00:17:48,260 --> 00:17:50,820
reveal the lack of decisiveness.

332
00:17:51,460 --> 00:17:52,700
Besides...

333
00:17:57,300 --> 00:17:58,140
Besides,

334
00:17:58,740 --> 00:18:01,780
Ministers Chen and Wang are inexperienced

335
00:18:02,300 --> 00:18:04,940
and not thorough enough.

336
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:08,940
Officials didn’t follow their relief plans.

337
00:18:09,580 --> 00:18:12,860
The result isn’t unexpected.

338
00:18:25,260 --> 00:18:26,500
The one who’s thorough

339
00:18:26,500 --> 00:18:28,020
and supported by all officials

340
00:18:28,900 --> 00:18:30,100
was accused

341
00:18:30,220 --> 00:18:32,380
of arbitrary

342
00:18:32,460 --> 00:18:34,740
and nepotism by censors

343
00:18:34,780 --> 00:18:35,860
for years

344
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:39,060
and just left the Capital due to his demotion.

345
00:18:41,460 --> 00:18:43,980
Now, Wang Sui and Chen Yaozuo are incapable.

346
00:18:45,180 --> 00:18:47,060
Wang Zeng and Lv Yijian are old

347
00:18:47,420 --> 00:18:48,460
and have left the Capital.

348
00:18:49,420 --> 00:18:52,300
Fan Zhongyan, although supported by scholars,

349
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:55,420
doesn’t fit to be Prime Minister.

350
00:18:59,380 --> 00:19:00,340
If I may,

351
00:19:03,180 --> 00:19:06,060
could Your Majesty write something for me?

352
00:19:08,780 --> 00:19:10,820
What is it?

353
00:19:12,780 --> 00:19:14,220
More is as bad as little.

354
00:19:20,060 --> 00:19:23,580
Since Wang Sui was appointed,

355
00:19:23,900 --> 00:19:24,980
he’s shown no talent

356
00:19:25,460 --> 00:19:26,900
at court

357
00:19:27,180 --> 00:19:28,460
but is known for his addiction

358
00:19:28,460 --> 00:19:29,900
to religion and witchcraft.

359
00:19:29,900 --> 00:19:30,980
How ridiculous!

360
00:19:30,980 --> 00:19:32,700
When the state was struck by the disaster,

361
00:19:33,140 --> 00:19:35,340
and His Majesty needed advice,

362
00:19:35,380 --> 00:19:36,980
rather than contributing to it,

363
00:19:36,980 --> 00:19:38,060
he claimed to be ill to avoid court appearances,

364
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:39,660
rested in the Cabinet

365
00:19:39,660 --> 00:19:42,020
and promoted his friends and family.

366
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:47,220
Zhigui, that's sharp!

367
00:19:49,060 --> 00:19:50,620
With such officials,

368
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:52,900
won’t His Majesty fear

369
00:19:53,860 --> 00:19:55,140
that others will follow suit?

370
00:19:55,780 --> 00:19:57,180
If our neighbors hear this,

371
00:19:58,380 --> 00:19:59,900
they’ll look down on our state.

372
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:10,300
It’s all true,

373
00:20:11,540 --> 00:20:12,220
but,

374
00:20:13,660 --> 00:20:15,340
if Prime Minister is deposed,

375
00:20:16,140 --> 00:20:17,460
who can take that position?

376
00:20:20,980 --> 00:20:22,260
In this time

377
00:20:23,940 --> 00:20:25,460
of internal and external crises,

378
00:20:26,380 --> 00:20:27,940
officials qualified for that post...

379
00:20:30,180 --> 00:20:31,140
are no other but one.

380
00:20:37,700 --> 00:20:40,020
My...my father-in-law?

381
00:20:42,660 --> 00:20:44,700
Deputy Censor Yan is the best fit

382
00:20:45,180 --> 00:20:46,940
and he’ll lead the Ministries sooner or later.

383
00:20:47,340 --> 00:20:49,100
He’s also on the top of His Majesty’s list.

384
00:20:50,580 --> 00:20:51,940
But given the current situation,

385
00:20:53,780 --> 00:20:54,820
the timing is still not perfect.

386
00:20:59,660 --> 00:21:02,660
“I understand why the rules aren’t clear.

387
00:21:03,380 --> 00:21:05,940
The wise know too much, yet the unwise too little”.

388
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:10,100
“I understand why the rules aren’t followed.

389
00:21:10,140 --> 00:21:13,980
The able are above them; yet the unable below”.

390
00:21:18,100 --> 00:21:20,340
Confucius is right.

391
00:21:20,860 --> 00:21:23,220
Some have too much; the others too little.

392
00:21:24,660 --> 00:21:27,260
Fan Zhongyan is selfless

393
00:21:28,220 --> 00:21:29,940
but inflexible

394
00:21:30,260 --> 00:21:32,260
yet Xia Song isn’t selfless enough.

395
00:21:33,700 --> 00:21:34,860
Lv Yijian is wise

396
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:36,740
and sophisticated

397
00:21:37,060 --> 00:21:38,700
but manipulative.

398
00:21:39,540 --> 00:21:42,420
Chen Yaozuo isn’t his match.

399
00:21:42,980 --> 00:21:44,220
In other word,

400
00:21:45,180 --> 00:21:47,660
Lv Yijian is a successful

401
00:21:47,860 --> 00:21:48,940
and decisive politician.

402
00:21:49,540 --> 00:21:53,060
Xia Song is good with people.

403
00:21:53,420 --> 00:21:55,340
Fan Zhongyan is righteous

404
00:21:55,540 --> 00:21:58,020
and completely loyal.

405
00:21:58,860 --> 00:21:59,900
Not to mention

406
00:22:00,580 --> 00:22:02,700
Han Qi’s insight,

407
00:22:02,980 --> 00:22:05,260
Fu Bi’s thoroughness,

408
00:22:06,020 --> 00:22:07,460
Su Shunqin, Ouyang Xiu

409
00:22:07,460 --> 00:22:08,780
and Cai Xiang’s talents.

410
00:22:09,380 --> 00:22:12,380
The court is full of talents.

411
00:22:12,620 --> 00:22:15,780
All I see is hope.

412
00:22:21,100 --> 00:22:22,220
That does

413
00:22:22,980 --> 00:22:24,180
make sense.

414
00:22:24,700 --> 00:22:27,060
Officials have their strengthens

415
00:22:27,260 --> 00:22:28,300
and weaknesses.

416
00:22:28,980 --> 00:22:31,220
They can be too much or too little,

417
00:22:31,580 --> 00:22:33,940
But appointing officials

418
00:22:34,580 --> 00:22:35,980
according to the situation,

419
00:22:36,540 --> 00:22:39,540
and even having them complement each other

420
00:22:41,700 --> 00:22:43,900
are up to Your Majesty.

421
00:22:54,420 --> 00:22:55,500
Lv Yijian?

422
00:23:11,180 --> 00:23:12,300
We gave it our all

423
00:23:12,300 --> 00:23:13,380
to finally have him...

424
00:23:13,380 --> 00:23:14,100
Zimei,

425
00:23:15,140 --> 00:23:16,700
why did we try so hard

426
00:23:16,900 --> 00:23:17,860
to impeach him?

427
00:23:18,660 --> 00:23:20,620
He sided with allies to act against his enemies.

428
00:23:20,820 --> 00:23:22,460
And he abused his power

429
00:23:22,460 --> 00:23:24,580
to win officials over to control the court

430
00:23:24,580 --> 00:23:25,660
and establish his authority.

431
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:28,220
As for how he dealt with allies and enemies,

432
00:23:29,100 --> 00:23:30,660
if allies are those who are like-minded

433
00:23:30,980 --> 00:23:32,020
and enemies the opposite,

434
00:23:32,460 --> 00:23:33,420
whoever becomes Prime Minister

435
00:23:33,700 --> 00:23:34,900
will do the same.

436
00:23:36,260 --> 00:23:37,260
When Minister Lv was in charge,

437
00:23:37,580 --> 00:23:38,940
what worried us most was

438
00:23:39,580 --> 00:23:41,860
that he controlled the court

439
00:23:42,180 --> 00:23:43,580
and outshone His Majesty.

440
00:23:47,060 --> 00:23:48,820
Yet a decree of demotion

441
00:23:49,260 --> 00:23:50,740
made him leave the Cabinet

442
00:23:51,060 --> 00:23:52,100
and the Capital.

443
00:23:54,060 --> 00:23:57,140
That proves he wasn’t that powerful.

444
00:23:58,980 --> 00:24:00,300
Back then,

445
00:24:01,460 --> 00:24:02,540
he survived the impeachment only because

446
00:24:04,220 --> 00:24:05,780
His Majesty didn’t want to dismiss him

447
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:07,700
not because he dared not

448
00:24:08,100 --> 00:24:08,980
or he couldn’t.

449
00:24:38,860 --> 00:24:40,020
What’s with the rush?

450
00:24:41,260 --> 00:24:43,700
It’s still early. Lie down with me.

451
00:24:45,260 --> 00:24:46,940
My wife

452
00:24:49,020 --> 00:24:51,180
wouldn’t find this place.

453
00:24:55,300 --> 00:24:56,820
You’re afraid of her

454
00:24:57,820 --> 00:24:58,780
but I’m not.

455
00:25:02,500 --> 00:25:04,180
That girl Bihan

456
00:25:05,460 --> 00:25:07,380
needs to be watched closely.

457
00:25:08,820 --> 00:25:10,340
She is clearly in love

458
00:25:11,460 --> 00:25:12,500
and she’s bold.

459
00:25:13,060 --> 00:25:14,060
I don’t want her

460
00:25:14,340 --> 00:25:15,780
to cause me trouble.

461
00:25:18,060 --> 00:25:20,700
He’s seen all kinds of people

462
00:25:20,700 --> 00:25:21,980
and been through all sorts of things.

463
00:25:22,500 --> 00:25:25,060
What can't he get?

464
00:25:27,820 --> 00:25:30,700
But true love is rare.

465
00:25:31,780 --> 00:25:32,940
If not for that,

466
00:25:33,020 --> 00:25:34,260
however beautiful she is,

467
00:25:34,260 --> 00:25:35,540
she’d be ignored.

468
00:26:00,980 --> 00:26:02,660
This pendant is cheap.

469
00:26:03,620 --> 00:26:05,220
I couldn’t afford a better one before,

470
00:26:09,700 --> 00:26:12,340
but I gave you expensive ones afterward.

471
00:26:14,900 --> 00:26:16,180
You’re too careful.

472
00:26:17,340 --> 00:26:19,460
You fear others will notice anything?

473
00:26:24,100 --> 00:26:26,060
= Xia Song, courtesy name Ziqiao =

474
00:26:26,060 --> 00:26:27,860
People all say Empress is tender.

475
00:26:28,980 --> 00:26:29,980
= Jia Yulan =
I don’t think

476
00:26:30,780 --> 00:26:32,660
she’s as soft as she seems.

477
00:26:34,140 --> 00:26:35,220
Bihan

478
00:26:35,860 --> 00:26:37,380
is so childish.

479
00:26:38,580 --> 00:26:40,540
She only met him once years back,

480
00:26:41,660 --> 00:26:43,300
but she was eager to find him.

481
00:26:44,100 --> 00:26:46,660
And now,

482
00:26:47,180 --> 00:26:48,900
she’s obsessed with love

483
00:26:50,220 --> 00:26:51,780
and is clueless about other things.

484
00:26:54,460 --> 00:26:56,860
Obsession is what matters.

485
00:26:57,460 --> 00:26:58,900
In terms of talents and wisdom,

486
00:26:58,900 --> 00:26:59,860
other than the late Empress Dowager,

487
00:26:59,860 --> 00:27:01,660
no one is better than Cao Danshu.

488
00:27:05,540 --> 00:27:07,020
All members of the harem,

489
00:27:07,260 --> 00:27:08,420
concubines

490
00:27:08,420 --> 00:27:09,860
and servants included,

491
00:27:09,900 --> 00:27:11,580
all listen to her.

492
00:27:12,620 --> 00:27:13,940
Other than that,

493
00:27:15,540 --> 00:27:17,380
the late Empress Dowager

494
00:27:17,740 --> 00:27:19,700
didn’t have a decorated grandfather,

495
00:27:19,900 --> 00:27:21,940
an uncle with the title Wumu

496
00:27:22,580 --> 00:27:24,740
or a teacher

497
00:27:24,740 --> 00:27:27,300
who’s considered a spiritual leader.

498
00:27:29,100 --> 00:27:30,380
Do you mean

499
00:27:30,660 --> 00:27:31,620
that stubborn girl

500
00:27:31,900 --> 00:27:33,260
has no chance at all?

501
00:27:36,820 --> 00:27:37,820
In this world,

502
00:27:37,820 --> 00:27:39,780
wisdom is most useless

503
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:42,860
in love and relationships.

504
00:27:44,300 --> 00:27:46,780
Who can read His Majesty’s mind?

505
00:27:47,260 --> 00:27:48,620
Lv and Fan are enemies for years.

506
00:27:49,180 --> 00:27:51,260
Fan seems to be on the moral high ground,

507
00:27:51,260 --> 00:27:53,380
but he’s promoted and demoted three times.

508
00:27:54,020 --> 00:27:55,940
Lv seems to be invincible

509
00:27:56,380 --> 00:27:57,540
but who’d know

510
00:27:57,540 --> 00:27:58,860
he’d be embarrassed

511
00:27:58,860 --> 00:28:00,580
by a waiter.

512
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:05,140
Fate is fickle.

513
00:28:05,140 --> 00:28:06,540
No one can predict the future.

514
00:28:08,700 --> 00:28:10,140
We’re only helping

515
00:28:10,140 --> 00:28:11,940
your adopted daughter

516
00:28:13,100 --> 00:28:15,460
to realize her dream.

517
00:28:18,260 --> 00:28:21,020
Thank you for your kindness.

518
00:28:24,700 --> 00:28:25,620
I'm leaving.

519
00:28:29,060 --> 00:28:30,540
If you need help,

520
00:28:30,980 --> 00:28:32,820
Yang Huaimin can be trusted.

521
00:28:45,860 --> 00:28:48,660
The rain is annoying.

522
00:28:49,380 --> 00:28:50,380
I feel cold.

523
00:28:54,300 --> 00:28:55,500
I have an appointment with Wen Yanbo

524
00:28:55,660 --> 00:28:56,900
and the landlady of the Restaurant of Breeze

525
00:28:56,940 --> 00:28:57,940
to discuss business.

526
00:28:58,060 --> 00:28:58,940
We can

527
00:28:58,940 --> 00:29:00,340
have some warm liquor

528
00:29:00,500 --> 00:29:01,340
to warm the body.

529
00:29:09,060 --> 00:29:10,260
This boy

530
00:29:11,500 --> 00:29:12,740
must’ve practiced calligraphy.

531
00:29:13,820 --> 00:29:15,260
Few at this age

532
00:29:15,980 --> 00:29:17,420
have his calmness.

533
00:29:18,140 --> 00:29:19,980
His family must’ve collapsed or be punished

534
00:29:20,380 --> 00:29:21,460
that he ended up here.

535
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:22,740
What a shame!

536
00:29:35,180 --> 00:29:37,420
Censor Han, I’ve finished.

537
00:29:52,060 --> 00:29:53,140
Your handwriting is good.

538
00:29:53,660 --> 00:29:54,500
You’re focused

539
00:29:54,860 --> 00:29:56,020
and I like your personality.

540
00:29:57,260 --> 00:29:58,860
I’ll tell Officer Ren tomorrow

541
00:29:59,180 --> 00:30:00,500
to transfer you to the Imperial Study

542
00:30:00,940 --> 00:30:02,060
to handle the paperwork.

543
00:30:03,060 --> 00:30:04,660
It’s not heavy labor,

544
00:30:05,260 --> 00:30:06,700
but you need to read more books,

545
00:30:06,980 --> 00:30:07,820
so you won’t be free.

546
00:30:08,460 --> 00:30:09,260
Do you want to come?

547
00:30:11,700 --> 00:30:14,340
I’ll listen to Officer Ren.

548
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:41,430
♪ Have no mood to color the eyebrows ♪

549
00:30:41,480 --> 00:30:48,080
♪ Pack up the clothes for your trip ♪

550
00:30:48,140 --> 00:30:55,210
♪ Dare not make you sad ♪

551
00:30:55,700 --> 00:31:01,740
♪ Struggle to hold tears back ♪

552
00:31:08,990 --> 00:31:14,910
♪ Have no mood to color the eyebrows ♪

553
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:21,430
♪ Pack up the clothes for your trip ♪

554
00:31:21,510 --> 00:31:28,610
♪ Dare not make you sad ♪

555
00:31:29,060 --> 00:31:34,890
♪ Struggle to hold tears back ♪

556
00:31:35,010 --> 00:31:45,980
♪ So that I wouldn’t know when you leave ♪

557
00:31:58,260 --> 00:31:59,380
Years back,

558
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:02,340
when first hearing this poem about separation,

559
00:32:03,180 --> 00:32:04,180
I was overwhelmed.

560
00:32:05,540 --> 00:32:07,700
“I’d rather get myself drunk first

561
00:32:07,980 --> 00:32:09,820
so that I wouldn’t know when you leave”.

562
00:32:10,540 --> 00:32:11,660
One would rather be drunk

563
00:32:13,420 --> 00:32:15,340
when parting with

564
00:32:16,060 --> 00:32:16,860
the loved one.

565
00:32:17,300 --> 00:32:20,140
All to fool the broken heart.

566
00:32:21,100 --> 00:32:23,340
How sentimental!

567
00:32:24,740 --> 00:32:25,940
Those feelings of separation

568
00:32:26,780 --> 00:32:27,980
are penetrating.

569
00:32:30,780 --> 00:32:33,100
Xia Song is talented.

570
00:32:36,300 --> 00:32:37,660
Most of his early poems

571
00:32:38,380 --> 00:32:39,260
are masterpieces,

572
00:32:40,180 --> 00:32:43,540
= Wen Yanbo, courtesy name Kuanfu =
especially those about separations.

573
00:32:43,940 --> 00:32:45,580
They’re quite touching.

574
00:32:46,380 --> 00:32:47,340
Sadly,

575
00:32:48,300 --> 00:32:49,700
when I met him in person

576
00:32:50,260 --> 00:32:51,220
at court,

577
00:32:52,260 --> 00:32:53,740
I only saw a shameless,

578
00:32:54,100 --> 00:32:56,660
greedy and lascivious chunk.

579
00:32:58,180 --> 00:32:59,900
No one is better than Su

580
00:33:00,260 --> 00:33:02,220
who’s as graceful as his work.

581
00:33:09,700 --> 00:33:11,340
When I first met you over a decade ago,

582
00:33:11,980 --> 00:33:13,780
I still wasn’t in charge

583
00:33:14,260 --> 00:33:15,700
and you were only a commoner.

584
00:33:16,620 --> 00:33:18,980
You talked freely with me.

585
00:33:19,820 --> 00:33:21,900
Farming supports the state; business enriches it.

586
00:33:22,740 --> 00:33:25,620
If comparing farming, mine and machines

587
00:33:25,940 --> 00:33:28,620
to rich lakes and mountains,

588
00:33:28,940 --> 00:33:30,940
business will be the channel

589
00:33:30,940 --> 00:33:32,660
that links those places together.

590
00:33:32,980 --> 00:33:35,580
Then fish in one lake can eat grass in another.

591
00:33:36,060 --> 00:33:37,220
Trees of this mountain

592
00:33:37,260 --> 00:33:38,860
can be planted at other places.

593
00:33:39,020 --> 00:33:41,820
That way, all beings will prosper.

594
00:33:44,700 --> 00:33:45,580
I’m ashamed.

595
00:33:45,980 --> 00:33:48,020
I was too young and naive before.

596
00:33:49,700 --> 00:33:50,500
What about now?

597
00:33:52,380 --> 00:33:53,340
I still believe

598
00:33:54,140 --> 00:33:56,340
no business, no convergence,

599
00:33:57,500 --> 00:33:59,100
hence no prosperity.

600
00:34:02,700 --> 00:34:04,180
About your ambition,

601
00:34:04,780 --> 00:34:06,740
your thoughts and plans,

602
00:34:07,140 --> 00:34:08,020
I understand them

603
00:34:09,380 --> 00:34:13,180
and I have eyes and my own judgment.

604
00:34:13,980 --> 00:34:15,100
The core

605
00:34:16,140 --> 00:34:16,980
of the traditional laws

606
00:34:16,980 --> 00:34:18,820
emphasizes the national and public interests.

607
00:34:19,540 --> 00:34:20,940
If that can be achieved,

608
00:34:21,540 --> 00:34:23,740
what kind of trees should be planted,

609
00:34:24,060 --> 00:34:26,180
whether business should be supported or not

610
00:34:26,540 --> 00:34:27,580
can be decided accordingly.

611
00:34:28,340 --> 00:34:29,580
All that can benefit the state and the people

612
00:34:30,020 --> 00:34:32,500
fit traditional laws.

613
00:34:34,660 --> 00:34:38,820
I’m honored to serve you, Your Majesty.

614
00:34:41,060 --> 00:34:42,340
But only with

615
00:34:42,940 --> 00:34:44,420
the right time

616
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:45,700
and people

617
00:34:45,980 --> 00:34:47,300
can the laws be made properly.

618
00:34:48,140 --> 00:34:50,020
Success requires unity.

619
00:34:51,060 --> 00:34:52,500
What I’ve learned most

620
00:34:52,900 --> 00:34:54,100
over the past 16 years of ruling

621
00:34:54,780 --> 00:34:56,100
is to be patient.

622
00:34:58,780 --> 00:35:02,100
You're intelligent and talented.

623
00:35:02,860 --> 00:35:03,900
You're more capable

624
00:35:04,060 --> 00:35:05,500
than most people.

625
00:35:06,140 --> 00:35:07,460
If you can have more patience,

626
00:35:08,180 --> 00:35:11,020
I’ll have one more pillar at court.

627
00:35:26,260 --> 00:35:26,940
Zhigui,

628
00:35:28,060 --> 00:35:28,980
three days ago,

629
00:35:29,740 --> 00:35:31,340
your proposal criticizing ministers

630
00:35:31,380 --> 00:35:32,140
was submitted.

631
00:35:32,900 --> 00:35:35,540
His Majesty said yesterday to discuss it today.

632
00:35:36,460 --> 00:35:37,460
So this is it.

633
00:35:39,740 --> 00:35:41,420
Criticizing four ministers in your proposal,

634
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:43,300
you’re bolder than Fan Xiwen.

635
00:35:44,980 --> 00:35:46,380
I wonder what will happen

636
00:35:46,700 --> 00:35:47,820
later at court.

637
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:51,540
As long as His Majesty

638
00:35:51,780 --> 00:35:53,540
won’t throw me out and imprison me,

639
00:35:54,300 --> 00:35:56,100
I won’t kill myself to send a message.

640
00:35:57,740 --> 00:35:58,660
I simply expressed my views.

641
00:35:59,340 --> 00:36:00,500
It’s up to His Majesty to decide.

642
00:36:04,740 --> 00:36:05,940
I admire your calmness most.

643
00:36:09,700 --> 00:36:10,500
I’m faking it.

644
00:36:12,660 --> 00:36:13,940
I’m unlikely to be imprisoned

645
00:36:14,860 --> 00:36:16,500
but a demotion is possible.

646
00:36:18,660 --> 00:36:19,460
If that’s the case,

647
00:36:20,140 --> 00:36:22,020
remember to see me off with liquor.

648
00:36:25,340 --> 00:36:26,100
I’m speechless.

649
00:36:43,620 --> 00:36:44,340
Miss,

650
00:36:45,060 --> 00:36:47,020
let me call an Imperial Physician.

651
00:36:47,980 --> 00:36:49,220
I simply caught a cold.

652
00:36:50,380 --> 00:36:53,420
After the earthquake and heavy rains,

653
00:36:54,140 --> 00:36:55,940
I was too worried to sleep well.

654
00:36:59,980 --> 00:37:00,780
I already prescribed

655
00:37:00,780 --> 00:37:01,780
myself medicine

656
00:37:01,780 --> 00:37:02,820
and took it with the meal.

657
00:37:02,860 --> 00:37:04,020
I’ll be fine in a few days.

658
00:37:05,140 --> 00:37:06,260
You know my condition.

659
00:37:06,540 --> 00:37:08,460
Thanks to my martial arts practice, I’m strong.

660
00:37:09,380 --> 00:37:10,620
There’s no need to call the physician.

661
00:37:14,180 --> 00:37:15,740
You're strong

662
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:16,820
yet already became sick.

663
00:37:17,260 --> 00:37:18,100
His Majesty...

664
00:37:22,060 --> 00:37:23,860
You have your job

665
00:37:25,180 --> 00:37:27,300
and mine is to manage the harem.

666
00:37:28,140 --> 00:37:29,420
There’s nothing to complain about.

667
00:37:32,060 --> 00:37:33,700
I only take care of the harem

668
00:37:34,780 --> 00:37:36,660
but His Majesty is much busier.

669
00:37:38,540 --> 00:37:40,380
He probably hasn’t had enough sleep lately.

670
00:37:42,980 --> 00:37:43,820
Indeed.

671
00:37:44,660 --> 00:37:45,820
Over the past few days,

672
00:37:46,260 --> 00:37:48,260
he’s been reading reports till midnight

673
00:37:48,580 --> 00:37:49,660
and got up at 2 a.m.

674
00:37:50,420 --> 00:37:52,100
Although he didn’t come here,

675
00:37:52,540 --> 00:37:54,060
no other women has he met.

676
00:37:54,660 --> 00:37:56,180
And he had no time

677
00:37:56,180 --> 00:37:57,140
for that dancer, either.

678
00:37:57,340 --> 00:37:58,540
Who taught you to gossip around

679
00:37:58,540 --> 00:37:59,500
behind others’ backs?

680
00:38:05,100 --> 00:38:06,300
Was it Liaozi?

681
00:38:07,460 --> 00:38:08,660
Or you taught him?

682
00:38:12,670 --> 00:38:13,310
I...

683
00:38:14,100 --> 00:38:15,060
I just noticed

684
00:38:15,660 --> 00:38:17,940
that His Majesty didn’t come

685
00:38:18,380 --> 00:38:19,460
even when you fell ill,

686
00:38:19,740 --> 00:38:20,420
so I...

687
00:38:22,740 --> 00:38:23,420
I...

688
00:38:26,580 --> 00:38:27,420
First,

689
00:38:29,660 --> 00:38:30,780
stop calling me the way you did

690
00:38:30,780 --> 00:38:32,020
when we were at home.

691
00:38:33,260 --> 00:38:35,140
Call me by the title

692
00:38:35,540 --> 00:38:36,540
as others do in the palace.

693
00:38:37,940 --> 00:38:39,620
In front of you is the Empress of Song,

694
00:38:40,420 --> 00:38:41,740
not Miss Cao anymore.

695
00:38:43,100 --> 00:38:46,620
Second, reflect on yourself.

696
00:38:47,820 --> 00:38:49,020
Don’t go outside

697
00:38:50,140 --> 00:38:51,340
or serve me.

698
00:38:51,900 --> 00:38:53,060
Don’t do anything

699
00:38:54,340 --> 00:38:55,740
except for copying the chapter Learning Rites

700
00:38:56,380 --> 00:38:57,740
in Principles for Women.

701
00:39:02,060 --> 00:39:02,780
Yes.

702
00:39:08,020 --> 00:39:08,860
Censor Han.

703
00:39:10,220 --> 00:39:11,020
Censor Han.

704
00:39:13,380 --> 00:39:14,300
Censor Han.

705
00:39:16,100 --> 00:39:17,740
Your report

706
00:39:18,100 --> 00:39:20,940
criticized four ministers’ nonfeasance.

707
00:39:21,100 --> 00:39:22,540
That’s unprecedented.

708
00:39:23,860 --> 00:39:25,500
In the end,

709
00:39:26,140 --> 00:39:28,860
they either resigned or were demoted.

710
00:39:30,780 --> 00:39:32,460
One report dismissed four ministers.

711
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:34,300
That will be remembered by history.

712
00:39:38,700 --> 00:39:40,660
I have no personal grudges against them

713
00:39:41,140 --> 00:39:42,580
and I’m only doing the job

714
00:39:42,740 --> 00:39:44,020
that I’m paid for.

715
00:39:45,340 --> 00:39:47,660
I simply expressed my views.

716
00:39:48,580 --> 00:39:49,900
Only His Majesty has the right to decide.

717
00:39:54,380 --> 00:39:56,820
A few days ago, I found broken bamboo slips

718
00:39:57,260 --> 00:39:58,740
with some characters.

719
00:39:58,900 --> 00:40:00,180
I looked into ancient records

720
00:40:00,180 --> 00:40:01,660
and racked my brain

721
00:40:01,860 --> 00:40:03,060
but failed to recognize them.

722
00:40:04,140 --> 00:40:05,380
Censor Han. Censor Han.

723
00:40:20,260 --> 00:40:22,340
I thought today’s court discussion

724
00:40:22,900 --> 00:40:23,700
would be

725
00:40:23,700 --> 00:40:25,020
fierce and filled with hostility.

726
00:40:25,180 --> 00:40:27,020
It would take at least a few hours.

727
00:40:27,060 --> 00:40:29,060
We wouldn’t be able to leave before sunset.

728
00:40:29,380 --> 00:40:31,380
Yet the four ministers were deposed yesterday

729
00:40:31,980 --> 00:40:33,620
and today’s morning court got canceled.

730
00:40:33,780 --> 00:40:34,900
Today’s discussion

731
00:40:35,100 --> 00:40:36,180
was only to tell the officials

732
00:40:36,180 --> 00:40:37,300
to learn from their lessons

733
00:40:37,460 --> 00:40:39,060
and to discuss detailed rules and regulations

734
00:40:39,060 --> 00:40:40,660
about internal and external affairs.

735
00:40:41,340 --> 00:40:43,580
Minister Wang and Minister Chen are old

736
00:40:43,660 --> 00:40:44,820
without serious mistakes.

737
00:40:45,140 --> 00:40:46,860
They’re only unqualified for being ministers.

738
00:40:47,060 --> 00:40:49,140
His Majesty wouldn’t allow them

739
00:40:49,140 --> 00:40:50,700
to be humiliated

740
00:40:50,740 --> 00:40:51,900
in public.

741
00:40:53,020 --> 00:40:55,420
Gentlemen can rise above their disagreements.

742
00:40:55,580 --> 00:40:58,580
Arguing in public is impolite.

743
00:40:59,060 --> 00:41:00,180
Words can be hurtful.

744
00:41:00,820 --> 00:41:02,140
If that becomes a routine,

745
00:41:02,740 --> 00:41:03,940
manners will be lost.

746
00:41:04,380 --> 00:41:06,900
His Majesty doesn’t want to see that happen.

747
00:41:08,620 --> 00:41:12,420
= Chen Mansion =

748
00:41:24,700 --> 00:41:26,820
Is there a decree for me?

749
00:41:27,700 --> 00:41:28,860
Only a message.

750
00:41:30,540 --> 00:41:31,540
His Majesty says

751
00:41:32,340 --> 00:41:34,420
you have always been righteous

752
00:41:34,700 --> 00:41:35,780
and fearless.

753
00:41:36,300 --> 00:41:38,100
As the local governor,

754
00:41:38,140 --> 00:41:39,940
you were excellent in managing the water.

755
00:41:40,340 --> 00:41:42,580
= Chen Yaozuo, courtesy name Xiyuan =
You stopped the Qiantang tide and the Yellow River flood,

756
00:41:42,740 --> 00:41:44,300
built dikes and planted willows to prevent floods,

757
00:41:44,500 --> 00:41:46,580
which benefited countless people.

758
00:41:46,900 --> 00:41:48,260
Your merits can’t be ignored

759
00:41:48,940 --> 00:41:51,060
and you’re definitely not incapable.

760
00:41:51,700 --> 00:41:53,140
Although you didn’t fit to be a minister,

761
00:41:53,900 --> 00:41:55,460
when Lv and Wang left

762
00:41:55,580 --> 00:41:57,180
and the Cabinet was leaderless,

763
00:41:57,620 --> 00:41:59,740
you filled in at your old age

764
00:41:59,900 --> 00:42:01,220
and worked tirelessly.

765
00:42:01,660 --> 00:42:02,860
Censor Han’s report

766
00:42:03,100 --> 00:42:04,460
was only about the current situation.

767
00:42:04,820 --> 00:42:07,020
It was nothing personal.

768
00:42:07,980 --> 00:42:10,700
Please don’t take it to heart.

769
00:42:11,500 --> 00:42:13,260
I failed in my duty

770
00:42:13,500 --> 00:42:15,540
and should be demoted,

771
00:42:15,940 --> 00:42:17,860
yet His Majesty sent you

772
00:42:18,180 --> 00:42:19,460
to comfort me.

773
00:42:20,300 --> 00:42:23,660
He’s too kind.

774
00:42:24,100 --> 00:42:25,740
I could only

775
00:42:26,140 --> 00:42:27,820
do my utmost to serve the people

776
00:42:28,260 --> 00:42:32,300
in Zhengzhou to repay his kindness.

777
00:42:39,660 --> 00:42:49,340
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

778
00:42:50,660 --> 00:42:59,020
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

779
00:43:01,860 --> 00:43:06,580
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

780
00:43:07,540 --> 00:43:11,700
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

781
00:43:13,140 --> 00:43:18,620
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

782
00:43:18,620 --> 00:43:23,420
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

783
00:43:27,100 --> 00:43:32,740
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

784
00:43:32,740 --> 00:43:37,620
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

785
00:43:38,140 --> 00:43:43,900
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

786
00:43:43,900 --> 00:43:48,980
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

787
00:43:49,420 --> 00:43:54,340
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

788
00:43:54,980 --> 00:43:59,820
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

789
00:44:00,500 --> 00:44:05,660
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

790
00:44:06,140 --> 00:44:11,180
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

791
00:44:11,740 --> 00:44:15,820
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

792
00:44:17,260 --> 00:44:21,900
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

793
00:44:22,940 --> 00:44:28,100
♪ The howling wind ♪

794
00:44:28,460 --> 00:44:32,540
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

795
00:44:34,020 --> 00:44:38,940
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

796
00:44:39,580 --> 00:44:44,820
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

797
00:44:45,220 --> 00:44:50,500
♪ The howling wind ♪

798
00:44:50,820 --> 00:44:55,700
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

799
00:44:56,300 --> 00:45:03,020
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
